		<title>SEC Grants Paxos Historic Approval to Clear and Settle US Equities on Blockchain</title>
		<link>https://news.bitcoin.com/sec-grants-paxos-historic-approval-to-clear-and-settle-us-equities-on-blockchain/</link>
		
